Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:56.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't call it assassination, Jango.\NThat has a bad ring to it. - Funi}Don't call it an assassination.\NThat has a bad ring to it, Jango.{T, changed to match VA}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Accident. It's an accident. - Funi}Accident. It'll be an accident.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, what're those guys talking about? - Funi}Hey, what are those\Nguys talking about?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-Don't look at me!{Funi}{D-Don't ask me! - Gord}{The OG felt more idiomatic but meant the same thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's what {\i1}I'd{\i} like to know!{Funi}{That's what I want to find out! - T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:11.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't simply kill her.{Funi}{We can't just kill her. - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:15.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Miss Kaya must perish\Nin an unfortunate accident. - Funi}Miss Kaya must pass away\Ndue to an unfortunate accident.{PP/T/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't mess that up! - Funi}You better not mess up!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:23.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So basically, on your signal, the men\Nand I storm the village and kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:27.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And then you'll get her inheritance... - Funi}{And you'll get her inheritance. - T}Then you'll get her inheritance.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You fool! You don't\Nunderstand a thing! - Funi}Imbecile! Use your head!{T/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How would I, an outsider,\Ninherit Kaya's estate?! - Funi}How could I, an outsider,\Ninherit Kaya's estate?!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll work hard to? - Funi}{You'll put in the work for it? - T}By working hard for it?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Working hard won't amount to squat. - Funi}Working hard is futile.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Listen, this is the most\Nimportant part!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Before you kill her, you'll use hypnosis\Nto make Kaya write her will... - Funi}Before killing her, you'll use hypnosis\Nto make Kaya write her will to say...{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to say: "I leave my entire fortune\Nto my butler, Klahadore!" - Funi}"I leave my entire fortune\Nto my butler, Klahadore!"{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:57.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Only then will I inherit\Nher enormous fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{in a completely ordinary manner. - Funi}in a completely legitimate manner.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:06.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've spent three long years gaining\Nthe trust of everyone around me, - Funi}I've spent three long years gaining\Nthe trust of everyone around her,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:10.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so that it would be unsurprising\Nfor her to leave her inheritance to me. - Funi}so no one would bat an eye when\Nshe leaves me her inheritance.{T/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three years as a butler for that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But you sure scared us back then, - Funi}You sure scared us back then,{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:23.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, you suddenly said\Nyou were giving up life as a pirate.{Three years ago, you up and said\Nyou were giving up life as a pirate. - T}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In no time flat, you set up\Na subordinate to be your double, - Funi}Just like that, you set up\Na subordinate as your double...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{then let the world see\NCaptain Kuro get executed. - Funi}and let "Captain Kuro" be\Nexecuted for the world to see.{T/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:45.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So that was the beginning of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You truly are Kuro,\NMan of a Thousand Plans. - Funi}You truly are Kuro\Nof a Thousand Plans.{T, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I abandoned that name\Nthree years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:56.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I now want to obtain great sums of money without the government on my back. - Funi}All I want now is to obtain vast riches\Nfree from government pursuit.{Gord+Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In other words, I'm a pacifist. - Funi}In other words, I'm a pacifist now.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Some pacifist you are! - CR}A "pacifist," he says!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:08.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{killing off an entire rich family\Nfor this "peace" of yours. - Funi}{Killing off a rich girl's\Nentire family for so-called peace. - T}{You call killing a rich girl’s entire family “peace”? - Gord}What kind of pacifist murders\Na rich girl's entire family?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The father's death was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I hadn't planned on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:14.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, whatever. - Funi}Oh well.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just hurry and give the signal. - Funi}Just give us the signal already.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:24.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've been waiting in the waters\Nfor almost a whole week now. - Funi}We've been waiting offshore\Nfor almost a whole week now.{T, Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The men are starting to grow impatient. - Funi}The men are starting to get antsy.{Polly/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.46,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is bad! - Funi}This isn't good!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.09,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{We heard something really bad! - Funi}We overheard something terrible!{PP+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?\NThat sounds kind of bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:46.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Weren't you listening this\Nwhole time?! This is seriously bad!}Weren't you listening?!\NThis is {\i1}seriously{\i} bad!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:55.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Captain Kuro is said to be the smartest and most brutal pirate of all! - Funi}{Captain Kuro is known as the smartest\Nand most brutal pirate of all! - T}Captain Kuro is known as the most\Ncunning and ruthless pirate of all!{Gord+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:00.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Rumor had it, the Marines caught\Nand executed him three years ago... - Funi}I'd heard the Marines caught\Nand executed him three years ago...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but Captain Kuro is alive! - Funi}but Captain Kuro is alive...{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As Klahadore, the butler! - Funi}as Klahadore, the butler!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:10.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's been after Kaya's fortune\Nfor these past three years! - Funi}He's been after Kaya's fortune\Nfor the past three years!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're gonna attack the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kaya's in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bad! - Funi}This is bad!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't stand up!\NThey'll see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't attack that girl! - Funi}Leave that girl alone!{WF}
Comment: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,[]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who're you?! - Funi}Who's there?!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You idiot! They spotted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hurry and hide before they kill you! - Funi}Quick! Hide before they kill you!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:40.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh... - Funi}Well...{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Usopp{-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They spotted me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you... hear anything? - Funi}Hear anything... interesting?{T/WF/Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{N-No! Whatever do you mean?! - Funi}N-No! Wh-Whatever do you mean?!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We just got here, so of course\Nwe didn't hear anything! - Funi}We just got here, so we\Ncouldn't have heard any–{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you! - Funi}Hey!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, all right. - T}All right, all right...{T/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you guys! - Funi}{Hey, dummies! - Polly}Hey, blockheads!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Watch this ring closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad! It's a throwing\Nweapon! Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{At the count of "one, two, Jango,"\Nyou will get sleepy.}{At the count of "one, two,\NJango," you will get sleepy. - T}On the count of "one, two,\NJango," you'll get very sleepy.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}One...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hide! He's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up, Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Have you still not fixed\Nthat habit yet?! - Funi}Have you still not fixed that habit?!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what're you doing?!\NYou're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, head-first... - Funi}Man, head-first, huh?{PP/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but he couldn't have\Nsurvived from that height... - Funi}but there's no way\Nhe survived that fall...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! - Funi}Dammit!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! - Funi}Dammit!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What about the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shall I take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter what he does,\Nit won't matter. - Funi}Whatever he does\Nwon't make a difference.{T}{10:12}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.{10:15, 16:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Attack the village at daybreak.{10:16, 16:59}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tear up the villagers' homes, - Funi}Ransack the villagers' homes,{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:21.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,and make certain Miss Kaya's\Nmurder looks like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You heard me, Usopp-kun. - Funi}That's how it is, Usopp.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:31.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's nothing you can do\Nto stop my plan. - Funi}No matter what you heard,\Nyou can't stop my plan.{Polly+PP+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! - Funi}Dammit!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You sure about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course. My plans are flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.07,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is bad, this is bad, this is bad! - Funi}This is bad! This is really, {\i1}really{\i} bad!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.49,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone in this village, who I\Ngrew up with, is going to be killed! - Funi}Everyone I grew up with\Nis going to be killed!{T, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.58,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kaya's going to be killed! - Funi}Kaya is going to be killed!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.62,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even though I love them all! - Funi}Everyone I love!{T, Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.38,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm Usopp! - Funi}The name's Usopp!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.05,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{A brave warrior of the sea! - Funi}I'm a brave warrior of the sea!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.17,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hear you've been unhappy lately! - Funi}I hear you've been down lately!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.22,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll cheer you up with a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.59,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.60,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.36,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,982)}I'll call for someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.27,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,And then? What happened after that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.02,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}I fought, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! - Funi}Dammit!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wasn't Luffy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Where's Luffy...? - Funi}Where's Luffy? Didn't you\Ngo to the shore toge...{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:52.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is he still mad about\Nhis dad being insulted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who knows. - Funi}Who knows?{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, that look was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something must've happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why do you suppose he\Nlooked so desperate?! - Funi}What could've freaked\Nhim out like that?{PP/WF}{TL - horrified}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, how do we get\Nto this shore of yours? - Funi}Hey, how do we get to that shore?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this smell like trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, something must've\Nhappened at the shore! - Funi}Yeah! Something\Nwent down at the shore!{T, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I think this calls for the Usopp Pirates! - Funi}This is a job for the Usopp Pirates!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright, already!\NHow do we get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Terrible news, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:27.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pirates are going to attack! - Funi}The pirates are coming!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tomorrow morning, pirates are\Ngoing to attack this village! - Funi}Pirates are going to raid\Nthis village tomorrow morning!{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, run away! - Funi}Run away, everyone!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're gonna pay once and for all! - Funi}We'll shut you up for good!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's the truth this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:08.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shut up! All you ever do\Nis spout huge lies!{17:38}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you were as honest as Klahadore(-san),\Nthen we'd believe you! - Funi}If you were as honest as Klahadore,\Nmaybe we'd actually believe you!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.09,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(17,767,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}{No matter what he does,\Nit won't matter. - Funi}Whatever he does\Nwon't make a difference.{T}{07:04}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.68,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.{07:10, 16:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Attack the village at daybreak.{07:12, 16:59}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.06,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! - Funi}Dammit!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:26.23,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{So he ignored me because\Nnobody would believe me anyway?! - Funi}{So he ignored me because he knew\Nno one would believe me?! - Gord}So he let me go... because\Nhe knew no one would believe me?!{WF+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are these to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're the ones you custom-ordered\Nfrom the eyewear shop... - Funi}I picked up the glasses\Nyou custom-ordered...{PP/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{in the next town over. - Funi}{from the neighboring\Ntown's eyewear shop. - PP}from the next town over.{Z - tightened up}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking you\Nto go all the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's a present, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Tomorrow will be three years, since the day\NKlahadore came to this mansion. - Funi}Tomorrow will be three years since\NKlahadore came to this mansion.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's always taken\Ngood care of me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Klahadore{-san} will be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:07.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes! - Funi}{Yeah! - Polly}He will!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please hear me out, everyone! - Funi}Everyone, please listen to me!{T/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pirates really [/i1]are[/i0] going to\Nattack tomorrow morning! - Funi}Pirates really will attack\Ntomorrow morning!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:21.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we believed every story you ever told, we'd have fled the village hundreds of times by now! - Funi}{\q2}If we believed every one of your tall tales,\Nwe'd have fled hundreds of times by now!{WF/T}{CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please, believe me! We gotta get out of here! - Funi}Please believe me!\NYou gotta get out of here!{T+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They really {\i1}are{\i0} going to kill everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:30.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I swear it's the truth this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}we're{\i} gonna get {\i1}you{\i0} this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's truly been three long years. - Funi}It's truly been a long three years.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Once this plan succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:01.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I intend to give you all\Nplenty of the take. - Funi}I intend to give you all\Na fair share of the plunder.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{At dawn tomorrow, destroy the village to your hearts' content! - Funi}At dawn tomorrow, ransack the village\Nto your hearts' content!{Gord/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! They're going to kill Kaya-san?!}{\q2}– What?! They're going to kill Miss Kaya?!\N– What?! They're going to kill Miss Kaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}– Are they really going to attack the village?!\N– Are they really going to attack the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's what they said. No question about it. - Funi}That's what they said.\NNo doubt about it.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So what were you\Nsleeping down here for? - Funi}So what were you doing\Nsleeping down here?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thought I was up on the cliff... - Funi}I thought I was on top of the cliff...{T, Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.03,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So how'd I get down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I knew it, Klahadore's a bad guy! - Funi}We were right! Klahadore's a bad guy!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No wonder he seems so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So that's why our captain ran to\Nthe village with that intense look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's great, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now they'll know and can\Nrun away beforehand! - Funi}They have time to escape now\Nthat they've been warned.{Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Talk about stupid bad guys! - Funi}Talk about dumb bad guys!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!\NWe gotta run away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, we better grab\Nall our prized possessions... - Funi}Yeah, we better grab our valuables...{T, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– ...and hurry!\N– ...and hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What is it? - Funi}What?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, we need to stock up on food\Nbefore the meat shop guy runs away! - Funi}We need to stock up on food\Nbefore the meat shop guy runs away!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's not the issue at hand here. - Funi}That's not the problem here.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought you might\Nnever come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You gotta run, Kaya!{SV04 @04:06}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about? - Funi}What do you mean?{T, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You've been tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your butler is really a pirate! - Funi}Your butler is actually a pirate!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I heard it with my own ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Klahadore's really a pirate... - Funi}Klahadore's a pirate...{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{who weaseled his way into your\Nmansion so he could get your fortune! - Funi}{who weaseled his way into\Nthis mansion to get your fortune! - PP}who weaseled his way into\Nthis mansion to steal your fortune!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:15.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's been pretending to be a butler for three years straight, just so he could rob you! - Funi}{\q2}He's been pretending to be a butler for\Nthree whole years just so he could rob you!{Griff/WF/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Usopp{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:25.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He said his crew's gonna storm in\Nand kill you at dawn tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's a really bad guy!\NYou gotta escape, quick! - Funi}This guy's as bad as they come!\NYou gotta escape, quick!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I admit, he did say too much earlier. - Funi}I admit, he did go too far earlier.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But lying like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's not like you, Usopp{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.30,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tell me, Usopp-san... - Funi}{So... tell me Usopp... - Z}So...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tell me, Usopp-san - Funi}{So... tell me Usopp... - Z}tell me, Usopp...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:12.39,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,What kind of story\Ndo you have today?{Kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.81,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Right. - Funi}Hmm...{Kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.10,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Right. Hmm, let's see... - Funi}Let's see... Today...{Kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.86,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.48,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:23.32,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,This story happened when I was five...{Kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:40}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:28.28,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{when I fought a giant goldfish\Nliving in the southern sea! - Funi}I fought a giant goldfish\Nthat lived in the south seas.{kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.95,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Goldfish? - Funi}A goldfish?{kind of a flashback to SV01 - 15:45}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.44,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,You fought a goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.46,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was so big,\Nnot even a fish tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.28,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,the size of this mansion\Ncould've held it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.35,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:56.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I loved the lies you told...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yet, why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:06.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's not like that! I'm not trying\Nto get back at Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why do you say it? - Funi}So why say it...?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kaya... I'm... - Funi}Kaya... I...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You gotta escape, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let go of her! - Funi}Unhand her this instant!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You gotta get out of this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,before that butler gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This'll all make sense come tomorrow! - Funi}This will all make sense tomorrow!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But you gotta escape for now!{SV04 @04:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.{Funi}{You're the worst - PP}{17:34}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:53.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He roughed up the lady of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How could he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.98,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{won't anyone believe me? - Funi}Why won't anyone believe me?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp{-san}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please pull yourself together, miss! - Funi}Please maintain\Nyour composure, miss!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, Jango.{07:10, 10:15}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.22,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Attack the village at daybreak!{07:12, 10:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Captain!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Y-You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This guy was asleep the whole time! - Funi}He was asleep this whole time!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and tell everyone\Nabout the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.92,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.{Funi}{You're the worst. - PP}{15:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.80,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Shut up! All you ever do\Nis spout huge lies!{10:04}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm lying like usual, obviously! - Funi}I'm lying as usual, obviously!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That damn butler pissed me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so I made up a lie about\Nhim being a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So the straw hat guy is in on it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:42.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd do that, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:45.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even if that butler {\i1}is{\i} a jerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I never thought you would lie\Njust to hurt someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We really respected you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's suppertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wonder what we're having...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why did you tell them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They were never going to\Nbelieve me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I was too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even so, the truth is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirates really are going\Nto come, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're definitely\Ngonna show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But everyone thinks its a lie. - Funi}But everyone thinks it's a lie.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:32.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They think tomorrow will be\Njust another normal, peaceful day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I'm going to stop the pirates at the beach\Ntomorrow and make sure this stays a lie! - Funi}I'm gonna stop the pirates at the beach\Ntomorrow and make sure it stays a lie!{T/Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the only logical thing\Nfor a liar like me to do! - Funi}That's the only thing that\Nmakes sense for a liar like me!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even if I get shot in the arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{or even if I'm driven off with brooms... - Funi}or driven off with brooms...{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{this is my village! - Funi}this is my home!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I love this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I want to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're one hell of a nice guy, - Funi}You're one hell of a good guy,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{pushing your crew away\Nand going into battle alone! - Funi}{to push away your crew\Nand go into battle alone. - T}pushing away your crew\Nand going into battle alone.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just so you know, I have dibs\Non all the pirates' treasure! - Funi}Just so you know, I call dibs\Non all the pirates' treasure!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright! We'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,are going to fight with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's a whole bunch\Nof bad guys, right? - Funi}Well, you're way outnumbered, right?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Scared" is written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me, scared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm perfectly okay with\Nlots of bad guys or whatever! - Funi}I'm perfectly fine against\Nlots of bad guys or whatever!{T+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:31.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because I'm Captain Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea! - Funi}After all, I'm Captain Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:39.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{These are Klahadore's pirates\Nwe're dealing with! - Funi}We're dealing with Klahadore's crew!{T/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't want your pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stop laughing, and leave! Leave! - Funi}Stop laughing and leave! Leave!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We ain't laughing! - Funi}We aren't laughing!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:51.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're impressed. That's why\Nwe want to help you! - Funi}It's commendable.\NThat's why we want to help you.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As if we'd risk our lives out of pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You guys...
